                </tr>
              </tbody>
            </table>
          </div>

          <p>Lux Jewels pricing is available on request — <a href="https://luxjewels.com/booking-appointment/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">book a free consultation</a> or a <a href="https://stan.store/luxjewels" target="_blank" rel="noopener">No-BS Call</a> to discuss your specific budget and requirements.</p>

          <p><em>Pricing subject to change. Confirm current rate at stan.store/luxjewels before booking.</em></p>

          <h2>Delivery to Toronto and the GTA</h2>

          <p>All Lux Jewels engagement rings ship via FedEx Priority, fully insured, with signature required on delivery. We don't ship rings without insurance and signature — there's no other way to do it responsibly.</p>

          <p>Typical delivery time to Toronto and the GTA is next-day from shipping date. For custom orders, production takes 4-6 weeks.</p>

          <p>We ship to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>All Toronto neighbourhoods (downtown, Midtown, North York, Etobicoke, Scarborough)</li>
            <li>GTA municipalities (Mississauga, Brampton, Markham, Richmond Hill, Oakville, Burlington)</li>
            <li>All Canadian provinces and territories</li>
            <li>United States</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Two Ways to Work with Lux Jewels as a Toronto Client</h2>

          <p><strong>Free Consultation — 30 to 40 Minutes</strong><br>
          Video call via Zoom or Google Meet. We'll discuss your style, stone preferences, and budget. I'll identify options and follow up with specific stone candidates and pricing. No commitment required.</p>

          <p><a href="https://luxjewels.com/booking-appointment/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="lj-btn lj-btn--primary">Book Your Free Consultation</a></p>

          <p><strong>No-BS Call — $199 for 30 Minutes</strong><br>
          You've already visited a Toronto showroom, received a quote, or found a specific stone online. You want a straight second opinion from someone with over 20 years in this industry.</p>

          <p>Bring the IGI certificate, the quote, the product link — whatever you have. I'll tell you exactly what it's worth, whether the stone is priced fairly, and whether there are better options at the same budget.</p>

          <p>The first and only service of its kind in the world.</p>

          <p><em>Pricing subject to change. Confirm current rate at stan.store/luxjewels before booking.</em></p>

          <p><a href="https://stan.store/luxjewels" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="lj-btn">Book a No-BS Call</a></p>

        </div>
      </div>
